premise_source_doc_sentence: Stefani released her second album The Sweet Escape in December 2006 ; it spawned five singles from October 2006 to October 2007 .

On the same day as Stefani released The Sweet Escape , she also released Harajuku Lovers Live on DVD , a recording of a concert performed in November 2005 in Anaheim , California as part of her Harajuku Lovers Tour .
`` The Sweet Escape '' was released as the album 's second single on December 19 , 2006 and was commercially successful in mainstream and adult contemporary markets .
`` The Sweet Escape '' is a song by American singer and songwriter Gwen Stefani from her second studio album of the same name  (  2006  )  .
The second single , `` The Sweet Escape '' , featuring rapper Akon , peaked in the top 10 of most charts , reaching number two in the US and UK .
